"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The president of the US has warned on social media that the country will target Iran's power plants and bridges if they cannot reach an agreement.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President's Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. ha advertido en redes sociales que el pa\u00eds atacar\u00e1 las plantas de energ\u00eda y puentes de Ir\u00e1n si no llegan a un acuerdo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia del Presidente de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Shreveport, Louisiana, a tragic incident occurred where children aged one to 14 years old were killed in a shooting. The police are calling it a domestic disturbance.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tragic Shooting in Louisiana\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Shreveport, Louisiana, ocurri\u00f3 un incidente tr\u00e1gico donde ni\u00f1os de uno a 14 a\u00f1os murieron en un tiroteo. La polic\u00eda lo llama un disturbio dom\u00e9stico.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tiroteo Tr\u00e1gico en Louisiana\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Residents near a device were evacuated from their homes while authorities worked to neutralize it. The evacuation covered a 450-meter radius.\",            \"english_title\": \"Evacuation Due to Device\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los residentes cerca de un dispositivo fueron evacuados de sus casas mientras las autoridades trabajaban para neutralizarlo. La evacuaci\u00f3n cubri\u00f3 un radio de 450 metros.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Evacuaci\u00f3n por Dispositivo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ben Roberts-Smith has made his first public statement after being charged with five counts of murder related to war crimes last week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ben Roberts-Smith's Statement\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ben Roberts-Smith hizo su primera declaraci\u00f3n p\u00fablica despu\u00e9s de ser acusado de cinco cargos de asesinato relacionados con cr\u00edmenes de guerra la semana pasada.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Declaraci\u00f3n de Ben Roberts-Smith\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"An attacker who took hostages in a supermarket was killed in a shoot-out with police, according to officials.\",            \"english_title\": \"Supermarket Hostage Situation\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un atacante que tom\u00f3 rehenes en un supermercado fue muerto en un tiroteo con la polic\u00eda, seg\u00fan las autoridades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Situaci\u00f3n de Rehenes en Supermercado\"        }    ]}"